==Usage==

Just put:

{{tlu|Vandalized-combo}}

on your user page.  


'''Example:'''

{{tlu|Vandalized-combo|13}}

'''Displays:'''
{{vandalized-combo|13}}
<br style="clear:left;" />


'''You can also use it to declare you've never been vandalized, with a parameter of "0":'''

{{tlu|Vandalized-combo|0}}

{{vandalized-combo|0}}
<br style="clear:left;" />


'''Leaving off the number simply declares you've been vandalized, period:'''

{{tlu|Vandalized-combo}}

{{vandalized-combo}}
<br style="clear:left;" />


